name: Swag, Parental Advisory Only
description:
"Swag, Parental Advisory Only", 2021, digital collage of watercolor painting and digital elements - pixel filter

My works are pretty much influenced by movies, authors such as Joumana Haddad and big brands such as Barbie or the Bratz. I try to put them in roles that are not associated with "femininity" in our society. I want them to be badass girls, with long hair, makeup and short skirts.  I studied painting, but over the years I started creating collages and low-fi animations because I am desperate for interactive experiences. I need emotions more than technique.
